# FoundSounds (2015)

An international collaborative art project disguised as a social network (2010–2015).

- [More information](https://foundsounds.me)
- [FoundSounds API source](https://github.com/FoundSounds/FoundSounds-API)
- [FoundSounds iOS source](https://github.com/FoundSounds/FoundSounds-iOS)
- [FoundSounds web source](https://github.com/FoundSounds/FoundSounds-Web)

An international collaborative art project disguised as a social network, running from 2010 to 2015. FoundSounds invited people around the world to record, share, and recombine the sounds of their everyday environments.
